  "title": "PERSONAL & BUSINESS DEVELOPMENT REPRESENTATIVE (FRESH GRAD/ORD WELCOME)",
  "description": "<p><br />Are you driven, ambitious, and looking for more than just a 9–6 job? 🚀<br />We’re a <strong>face-to-face (F2F) marketing organisation</strong> helping clients generate revenue through people-first marketing strategies. As we expand locally and internationally 🌍, we’re looking for motivated individuals who want <strong>real growth, real exposure, and real rewards</strong>.</p><h3>💼 <strong>What You’ll Be Learning & Doing</strong></h3><ul><li>Learn the <strong>fundamentals of sales & effective communication</strong> 🗣️</li><li>Represent established clients through <strong>face-to-face marketing campaigns</strong></li><li>Build confidence, resilience, and strong people skills 💪</li><li>Learn how to <strong>manage a small team</strong>, with opportunities to grow into leading larger groups 👥</li><li>Gain exposure to <strong>business operations and leadership development</strong></li><li>Opportunities to <strong>travel overseas for business & expansion projects</strong> ✈️🌍</li></ul><h3>🙌 <strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></h3><ul><li><strong>No experience required</strong> — full training provided 📚</li><li>A <strong>charming, positive personality</strong> 😊</li><li>Strong drive for <strong>personal growth & self-development</strong></li><li>Enjoys working with people and in team environments</li><li>Coachable, open-minded, and motivated to succeed 🔥</li></ul><h3>⭐ <strong>Why Join Us</strong></h3><ul><li>Structured <strong>training & mentorship</strong></li><li>💰 <strong>Uncapped earning potential</strong> — your effort = your income</li><li>Clear and transparent <strong>career progression pathway</strong></li><li>✈️ <strong>Overseas travel opportunities</strong></li><li>Flexible scheduling with full-time stability</li><li>Energetic, supportive, and growth-oriented team culture 🤝</li></ul><p>If you’re in your 20s and looking for a role that offers <strong>growth, leadership, travel, and unlimited income potential</strong>, this could be the opportunity you’ve been looking for.<br /><br />APPLY NOW or contact Lester @ 9145 2411 for any further enquiries:)</p>",
